{"tid":1264561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩係現場見到林彥邦","createTime":"2019-06-28T17:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T18:46:41.000Z","uid":84396,"like":64,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fd7422b51cfdacc06c65a4c35a6464859ceca427","tid":1264561,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T17:59:19.000Z","msg":"憶述夢境：<br />\n<br />\n林生又係你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝每次都出黎為我地香港人報導事實<br />\n<br />\n岩岩同你講左句辛苦晒<br />\n<br />\n你答我職責黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，多謝你既工作報導我地200萬+1人為香港未來上街工作，多謝你既鏡頭保護住我地每個人<br />\n<br />\n職業係無高低之分，但品格係有貴賤之別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n狗仔們，唔好再同我講打返工啦，你地份工證明你地賤種黎，屌你地老母唔係無原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家要好好保護真正為香港既記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：捐左錢支持立場，無影到相希望保護返林生<br />\n<br />\n同埋，林生你幾型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">非gay</span>"},{"pid":"cf40054e2037730e47ee617293d2ff3881f5789d","tid":1264561,"uid":84396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:03:39.000Z","msg":"大家要好好多謝記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9451f79ab45bf677f7c36529cec85bac8e2156a8","tid":1264561,"uid":84396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:05:58.000Z","msg":"大家要好好多謝記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde3c193b23b45f8cba41ee28111282c770457be","tid":1264561,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:06:15.000Z","msg":"大家要好好多謝記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2de24824683e